John Voldstad https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Voldstad 0 John Ole Voldstad is an American television and film actor best known for his role as one of the brothers Darryl on Newhart. He played "my other brother Darryl", the one with the curlier, lighter colored hair.
